<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <!-- toast calendar -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://uicdn.toast.com/calendar/latest/toastui-calendar.min.css" />
    <script src="https://uicdn.toast.com/calendar/latest/toastui-calendar.min.js"></script>
    <!-- chart.js -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- font awesome -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/e13a984139.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- 합쳐지고 최소화된 최신 CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- 부가적인 테마 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
    <!-- 합쳐지고 최소화된 최신 자바스크립트 -->
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/slick-carousel/1.8.1/slick-theme.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/slick-carousel@1.8.1/slick/slick.css"/>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/slick-carousel@1.8.1/slick/slick.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
  
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dashboard.css">
    <script src="/js/dashboard.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="grid-wrapper">
        <nav class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo-container">내가 해냄</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/dashboard"><i class="icon fa-solid fa-house"></i>홈</a></li>
                <li><a href="/calendar"><i class="icon fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>달력</a></li>
                <li><a href="/accountbook"><i class="icon fa-solid fa-book"></i>가계부</a></li>
                <li><a href="/memo"><i class="icon fa-solid fa-file-pen"></i></i>메모</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="dashboard-container">
            <div class="dashboard-subgrid-container-left">
                <div class="dashboard-accountbook">
                    <div class="cover btn7">가계부로 해냄</div>
                    <div class="content-title" style="margin: 20px;">Account Book</div>
                    <canvas id="canvas" width="400px" height="200px" style="padding: 20px;"></canvas>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-memo">
                    <div class="cover btn7">메모로 해냄</div>
                    <div class="content-title">Memo</div>
                    <div class="memo-container"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dashboard-subgrid-container-right">
                <div>
                    <div class="dashboard-member-button">
                        <ul>
                            <li><button class="dashboard-button" onclick="location.href = '/userinfo'"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-gear"></i>마이페이지</button></li>
                            <li><button class="dashboard-button" onclick="location.href = '/'"><i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i>로그아웃</button></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-calendar">
                    <div class="cover btn7">달력로 해냄</div>
                    <div class="content-title" style="margin: 20px;">Calendar</div>
                    <div id="container">
                        <div id="header">
                          <div id="monthDisplay"></div>
                          <div>
                            <button id="backButton">Back</button>
                            <button id="nextButton">Next</button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="weekdays">
                          <div>Sunday</div>
                          <div>Monday</div>
                          <div>Tuesday</div>
                          <div>Wednesday</div>
                          <div>Thursday</div>
                          <div>Friday</div>
                          <div>Saturday</div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="calendar"></div>
                      </div>
                      <div id="newEventModal">
                        <h2>New Event</h2>
                        <input id="eventTitleInput" placeholder="Event Title" />
                        <button id="saveButton">Save</button>
                        <button id="cancelButton">Cancel</button>
                      </div>
                      <div id="deleteEventModal">
                        <h2>Event</h2>
                        <p id="eventText"></p>
                        <button id="deleteButton">Delete</button>
                        <button id="closeButton">Close</button>
                      </div>
                      <div id="modalBackDrop"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-guideline">
                    <div class="content-title" style="margin: 20px;">Guideline</div>
                    <div class="guideline-container">
                        <div class="guideline-content-container">
                            <div class="guideline-content">
                                1. 가계부를 통해서 자산관리에 힘써요!
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="guideline-content-container">
                            <div class="guideline-content">
                                2. 메모를 통해 중요한 일들을 기록해요!
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="guideline-content-container">
                            <div class="guideline-content">
                                3. 달력을 통해 메모와 가계부를 확인해요!
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>